Mumbai.name: Holiday Inn Mumbai Internationl
Mumbai.about: Situated just 2km from Chhatrapati Shivaji International Airport, the Holiday Inn Mumbai International Airport features a regular airport shuttle bus and free parking.Contemporary rooms each boast satellite television, iPod docks, a minibar and tea and coffee making facilities. Guests can upgrade their room to a suite to benefit from extended living space and club lounge access.

Mumbai.name: FabHotel Plaza Inn Andheri East
Mumbai.about: FabHotel Atlas Plaza Andheri East is suitably located on Old Nagardas Road near Chinai College.Many corporate hubs and offices like Akruti Trade Centre, Times Square, SEEPZ, The Crescent Business Park, Excom House, Hyde Park, Mirchandani Business Park, Akruti Orchid Park, Logitech Park, Millenium Plaza, Ansa Industrial Estate, and Prime Corporate Park are located a few minutes away.

Mumbai.name: The Leela Mumbai
Mumbai.about: Offering guests a world of comfort in Mumbai, FabExpress Liberty Plaza is popular among businesspersons and tourists alike. Its highlights include Closeness to Bandra-Kurla Complex and Mumbai airport.Charming rooms that add a touch of style to guests’ stay.Trained and hospitable staff which offers an exceptional service.

Mumbai.name: Courtyard by Marriott Mumbai
Mumbai.about: Courtyard by Marriott Mumbai International Airport is an upscale hotel that’s only three miles from Chhatrapati Shivaji International Airport.The air-conditioned rooms feature an ensuite with free toiletries, bathrobe, slippers and a hair dryer. Turndown service and daily housekeeping are standard as is a flat-screen TV, tea and coffee making facilities, minibar, and free bottled water. An in-room safe, phone, paid Wi-Fi, free newspaper, desk, and ironing set round off the room amenities.The hotel offers business and leisure guests a 24-hour front desk, 24-hour business centre, tour assistance, limo service, and dry cleaning and laundry facilities. For added convenience luggage storage, conference space, full spa with pool and fitness centre, and limited free parking are also offered.
